SUMMARY:Unity Industry User Day @ XR Symposium 2025
DESCRIPTION:Unity’s Industry team is thrilled to host an Industry User Day alongside the 2025 XR Symposium at Johns Hopkins University Applied Physics Laboratory (JHUAPL) in Laurel\, MD. Free to attend and open to the public. \nEvent Highlights\nWhen: July 10\, 2025\, 9:00 AM–5:30 PM (Industry User Day)\nWhere: 11091 Johns Hopkins Rd\, Laurel\, MD 20723 \nUnity Showcase:\n– Artist focused talks on high-fidelity asset pipelines and lighting techniques\n– Advanced optimization with Unity DOTS\n– Updates on Unity 6.2\n– CAD/BIM transformation via Unity Asset Manager\, and PiXYZ workflows with Unity Cloud Automation. \nThis event is perfect for anyone passionate about XR and immersive technologies. It’s a chance to see Unity’s latest tools in action and learn how they solve complex industry problems.\nRegister here: https://on.unity.com/3HokZuM
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/unity-industry-user-day-xr-symposium-2025/
LOCATION:JHU Applied Physics Lab\, 11091 Johns Hopkins Rd\, Laurel\, MD\, 20723\, United States
END:VEVENT
