SUMMARY:In-Person/Online Meetup
DESCRIPTION:In-person is at the Elkridge Branch Library in the Grist Mill Room. \nJoin us IN-PERSON or ONLINE. Anyone with an interest in game design and development is welcome\, from beginners to veteran professionals. \nWe will be meeting in the Marvin Thomas Room at the East Columbia Branch Library (6540 Washington Blvd\, Elkridge\, MD 21075). (Not an official Howard County Library System event.) \nIf you want to attend virtually\, the Discord server link is provided in the main monthly (1st of the month) meetup details. An organizer will ensure that a laptop is provided on-site to connect the Discord attendees with those physically on-site. It takes us a few minutes to set up the projector\, so hold tight when you join the Discord voice chat channel. We’ll be there soon!
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/in-person-online-meetup-2/
LOCATION:Elkridge Branch Library\, 6540 Washington Blvd\, Elkridge\, Maryland\, 21075\, United States
END:VEVENT
